    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks! I was thinking that match destructs the struct inside, so I can do smth like  <br>\n<code>LoggedIn(name, age)</code>  <br>\nsince I have background of langs with tagged unions in which fields can be attached directly to .. tag, not single opaque struct that need to be destructed.</p>",
